data.description: Here's your chance for a wonderful corner lot just under .5 acres in a great neighborhood in Springfield.  This 3 bdr 3 full bath ranch offers plenty of space to stretch out, new deck on the back, covered front porch and basement that can be used as a mother in law suite with kitchenette.  2 car garage in basement as well, 2 driveways offers plenty of parking with a bluff like view off the deck.  Schedule your today, you will want to see this home!
